data.description: Seize this opportunity for a substantial financial advantage! This home as a rare 2.75% interest rate with an assumable VA Loan. Enjoy a peace of mind that comes with this meticulously maintained home that offers modern elegance with quartz countertops, vaulted ceilings, and an insulated garage with a sink and ample storage. Wide hallways, open concept layout, and split bedrooms, this home has a spacious feel. Make the most of your summers with the 20-foot covered patio, easy to maintain backyard with full sprinkler system, and high fences and ensures privacy as you enjoy your outdoor haven. Beyond the home, the community offers a playground, tennis court, clubhouse, pool and is walking distance to Desert Sage Elementary. Act fast and schedule your appointment to view this home, it will not last long with everything it offers!
